    SeleniumElementsWrapper

    public abstract class SeleniumBrowserResourcesWrapper
extends ConfigurationAccess
    Selenium Wrapper around browser resources management (windows/tabs/alerts, cookies, screenshots and logs).

      • takeBrowserConsoleLogs

        public List<ValidationEntry> takeBrowserConsoleLogs(Level desiredLogLevel)
                                             throws RobotestException
        Returns a limited list of ValidationEntrys of WebDriver visible log from browser CONSOLE with desired level of any kind (JavaScript, CSS, network, etc). The retrived Level status equivalence is WARNING for WARNING, ERROR for > WARNING & INFO for < WARNING.
        Parameters:
        desiredLogLevel - log level desired
        Returns:
        The retrived browser CONSOLE log list
        Throws:
        RobotestException - Errors in the log retrive with web driver.
